Package: debian-admin-toolkit
Version: @VERSION@
Section: admin
Priority: optional
Architecture: all
Depends: bash (>= 5.0), whiptail
Recommends: dmidecode, lm-sensors, smartmontools, iproute2, fontconfig
Maintainer: grumel <grumel@gmail.com>
Homepage: https://github.com/grumel/debian-admin-toolkit
Description: Modular administration toolkit for Debian
 Debian Admin Toolkit (DAT) is a modular, whiptail-based administration
 toolkit for Debian 12 and Debian 13, for desktops and servers.
 .
 It bundles modules for system information, networking, desktop tweaks,
 software installation, maintenance and HTML reporting, and supports drop-in
 plugins. The toolkit is started with the "dat" command.
